
## Pet-Database Console-Based Application

## Description
This project is a very simple pet database management system that allows users to view, add and save pet information (name, age) with a unique ID associated with each pet. 


## Program features
- View all the pets in a clean formatted table.
- Add new pets to the database.
- Save the database to a txt file to write/read. 


## Usage
When you run the program, you will be presented with a menu:
1. View all pets
2. Add new pets
3. Exit Program


### Viewing Pets
- To view all pets, select option `1`.

### Adding Pets
- To add a new pet, select option `2`.
- Enter the pet details in the format: `name, age`.
- Type `done` to finish adding pets.

### Saving and Exiting
- To save the database and exit the program, select option `3`.


## Acknowledgments
- The list of 100 pet names and ages was generated using AI.

